name: Lilith (and the cat!)
description:
2022
Gif, collage of an original painting and digital elements

They tried to get rid of Lilith! I ain't kiddin'!
Someone sent a big kitty cat to bite into her neck.. 
NOT COOL! I know right?!
Anyways, these dummies didn't know that Lilith's evil ghost was hiding just behind her (see for yourself!!!)
And you really don't wanna mess with this... not so cute ghost!
